sql:
SELECT median_income_estimate
FROM household_income
WHERE year = 2021;

external_knowledge:
- "most recent year" refers to the latest year in the `household_income` table;
- "more than one income record" means the state has at least two income records in the dataset;
- "average median household income" is the mean of the median household income estimates for the state.

